Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.90,0:00:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.71,0:00:23.95,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.71,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.79,0:00:32.82,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:41.60,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.67,0:00:50.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.98,0:00:56.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.85,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.92,0:01:03.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.89,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.96,0:01:16.20,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.93,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.41,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.48,0:01:24.45,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.51,0:01:29.21,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.45,0:01:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破壞王都的惡魔又出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳錯了，柯蕾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是神的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.53,0:01:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我向您懺悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.53,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.57,0:01:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#24 守護者們的交響曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像陷入苦戰了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點跟我同步，賽內絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡被刺傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在一秒鐘都不能浪費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.01,0:02:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃到那片岩石區去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被刺到可是會死人的\N要小心一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等再自我介紹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來快點離開這裡比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們那邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法法兒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群叛國賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼止不住血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪烏傑魯神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您原諒帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您原諒帕希菲卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-帕希菲卡\N-夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-冷靜一點，夏儂\N-帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想一擊打倒他們是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在瞄準哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經到極限了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宰了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.03,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.44,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有我們\N被排除到大氣層之外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封棄世界進入了自我封閉模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是意料之外的狀況啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有辦法與系統取得聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我們的權限，限時解放能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德列克、露絲，盡全力防禦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲，使出所有的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.31,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.01,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部使出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.98,0:06:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露絲、露絲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還撐的住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，索柯姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.04,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.43,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...天堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是利用\N封棄世界管理系統的空白空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所做出來的虛擬實境世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.51,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳從肉體這個容器之中\N跑進了這個系統裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也死了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說\N妳到底是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希莉亞．瑪烏傑魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪烏傑魯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂，你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封棄世界怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於某種理由\N使得機能完全被凍結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和娜塔莉之間的通訊線路\N也處於被切斷的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是...神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是背叛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.75,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是這個\N封印人類世界的管理者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊，是為了破壞我而誕生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.33,0:09:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳身上那股花費16年所製造出來\N用來破壞我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被設定成會在妳死的時候啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳說我死的時候會啟動...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.78,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，距離完成為止\N似乎還差了10個小時左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在妳和我的力量剛好維持平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.82,0:09:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處在一種稍微刺激一下\N就會偏向其中一方的微妙狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...我希望由妳來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在妳出生的很久很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一場大規模的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭持續了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也死了很多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.98,0:10:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個時候\N敵人那邊傳給我一份訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.99,0:10:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了結束戰爭，保護人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我可以提供人類這邊的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.23,0:10:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從他們的觀點來看\N人類是非常珍貴的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.07,0:10:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想要讓\N將會自我毀滅的人類活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照他們說的去做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.88,0:10:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得這樣下去\N我的弟弟妹妹總有一天也會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.38,0:11:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後人類就被封閉在封棄世界裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我就被安裝到系統的中樞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5000年來一直維持著這個小世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是我的弟弟和妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.41,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們兩個人活著\N我就覺得很滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算人類被封閉在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們兩個人還能活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲，拜託妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝克納姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰術模式被敵人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲、葛羅莉亞、娜塔莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.18,0:11:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殘存的機體快點逃到異相空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們兩個人能夠活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳的肉體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.83,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳使用了14萬又150小時的容器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望由妳來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.31,0:12:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應不應該再這樣繼續下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我對人類\N還有世界的問題...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照妳的感覺去想就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是做錯了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有哥哥和姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果靠我的力量\N可以保護他們兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我會去做任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.12,0:13:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那要花上幾千年、幾萬年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.73,0:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，即使大家可以在\N被封閉的世界裡安全地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算選了一條不對的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是自己選的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為可以自己做出選擇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而從一開始就不能選擇的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是回答妳了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.96,0:13:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子，我就可以解脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解脫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！對不起，剛剛的不算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.91,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於可以到\N弟弟和妹妹那裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希莉亞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.55,0:14:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類啊，仔細聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑪烏傑魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收起手上的劍\N撤下你們的軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,災禍的根源已經消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.82,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後應該再也不會\N展現她的威力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門已經打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.43,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把自由、新的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有真正的天空還給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.74,0:15:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後應該也不會再下達神諭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要靠你們攜手合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙腳往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪烏傑魯不在天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在你們的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來要靠你們的雙手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己去創造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變態！變態！變態！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變態！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算看到妳的裸體\N我也沒感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你敢大大方方的看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧\N果然不敢，對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個悶聲色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發火之前應該先覺得害羞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個不知羞恥的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢說啊，你這個戀童癖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是戀童癖，妳這隻野貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看傷口...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.04,0:18:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請站起來吧，佛爾西斯殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.45,0:18:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡蘇魯兄妹他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說等等就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.99,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是\N佛爾西斯殿下的加冕儀式了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽內絲殿下他們也在等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.27,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柏拉赫夫婦更是早就出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.97,0:19:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德拉克諾夫就快要生了\N怎麼可以丟下牠不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.61,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟佛爾西斯說我下次再過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡，動作快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在過得幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼和平，每天又很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不全都是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那種事情\N就算現在不做決定也沒關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要死掉的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.02,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠覺得自己的人生\N還不算太糟糕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.53,0:20:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很慶幸自己生為廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有很多辛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過去過很多地方\N也認識了很多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是廢棄公主的話\N也不會認識雷歐你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.55,0:20:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一直都保護著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要重新對妳說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還早一百萬年咧，笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一等嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很愛妳啊，帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.98,0:21:35.82,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.89,0:21:41.16,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.23,0:21:48.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:54.20,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.27,0:21:59.14,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.68,0:22:07.59,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.65,0:22:14.12,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.49,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.86,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.93,0:22:27.40,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.47,0:22:34.14,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.21,0:22:39.55,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.62,0:22:46.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來